OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain first thing,
OL,6,Foccasionally heavy, will clear away
OL,7,Fsoutheastwards during the morning.
OL,8,FBrighter conditions with sunny spells
OL,9,Fsoon follow but also isolated,
OL,10,Fpossibly heavy showers. Any showers
OL,11,Ftending to ease during the afternoon.
OL,12,FWind easing. Cool.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA dry evening with sunny
OL,15,Fspells, but showers moving in from the
OL,16,Fnorthwest overnight, occasionally
OL,17,Fheavy with a low risk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
